 -- Steve Roscio <steve@HauntedMines.org>  Tue, 28 May 2013 12:13:17 -0600

hauntix (0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Daily ticketing feature added.
  * Added feature to not print receipts for cash-only sales.
  * Added feature: reprint last receipt.
  * Added feature: reprint last tickets.
  * Added Transaction lookup feature, with reprint receipt/tickets subfunctions.
  * Transaction & ticket void CLI utility added.
  * Improved ticket & transaction void function on POS.
  * Entry control keypad - backspace key added (requires Tk::NumKeypad 1.4+).
  * Daily web tickets time removed; just date shown now.
  * Only allow one copy of ourselves to run on a system (run_alone).
  * More relevant stats reported in info panel.
  * Show pickup code for last transaction in info panel.
  * Make info panel update on newsale, in addition to every 15 seconds.
  * Added badge check/use function.

 -- Steve Roscio <steve@HauntedMines.org>  Wed, 13 Oct 2012 15:02:17 -0600

